Class ClientPlayer

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.util.observer.ObservableObject<ModelListener>
it.polimi.ingsw.client.virtualModel.ClientPlayer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Observable<ModelListener>
public class ClientPlayer extends ObservableObject<ModelListener>
This class represents a single player in the virtual model. It aims to represent the state of a player in the client and update it if necessary
